                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold the R1 button and press Start 10 times, at the tenth press, hold Start until it's finished loading</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Unlock Sub Game -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enable Cheat Mode and then enter the following code as the game loads Up - Left - Down - Right</font>&nbsp;<br>
